title: DictVectoriser converter with string/int values throw error
body:
key_value_map = [{1: '1.0', 2: '2.0'}, {1: '11.1', 3: '13.1'}]
model = DictVectorizer(sparse=False).fit(key_value_map)
print(model.transform(key_value_map))

model_onnx = convert_sklearn(model, 'dv', [("input", DictionaryType(Int64TensorType([1]), StringTensorType([1])
                                                                                           ))])
onnxmltools.utils.save_model(model_onnx, 'dv.onnx')
sess = InferenceSession('dv.onnx')
res = sess.run(None, input_feed={'input': key_value_map[0]})
res
